org.factcenter.qilin.comm

Interface Channel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.DataInput, java.io.DataOutput, SendableInput, SendableOutput
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalChannelFactory.LocalChannel, TCPChannelFactory.TCPChannel

    public interface Channel
extends SendableOutput, SendableInput
    The Channel represents a point-to-point communication channel for sending and receiving data. Communication is guaranteed to be reliable and in order.
    See Also:
    LocalChannelFactory, TCPChannelFactory
